    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Exhibition curators are the creative leaders that conceptualize and mount exhibitions, and are distinguished from curators in general, who manage collections in museums, galleries, libraries, and other repositories.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
